N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 350.8 - Reexhibition in domestic department

State Regulations

No article shall be exhibited in the domestic department if
it has been previously exhibited therein, unless permitted by official action
of the board of directors of the fair sponsor. Notes
